Compose different


Recent research in AI-assisted music tools is opening new horizons for art creation. By learning on huge corpuses of existing sound pieces, a computer is able, on the one hand, to extract features from a sound and to learn notions such as structure, genre or even mood.  Composing music is a constantly evolving process. Indeed, from tribal percussions and rhythms to elkectronic dance music, composers have came a long way.